name: Valentine Cupid Poop
description:
This is a cute gag gift for Valentine’s Day!
Here is what it says 
I couldn’t send you flowers
And candy wouldn’t do
Mushy cards just didn’t say
The things I wanted them to
So I got you something special
And here is the inside scoop
I found you something very rare
It’s genuine Cupid Poop!

name: Mini Cinnamon Bun Tarts/Melts
description:
These mini cinnamon bun tarts are great for small tart burners or to add to potpourri & fixins.

	These tarts are scented in cinnabun buns with a strong caramel scented icing. You will receive a pkg of 15.

name: Valentine Heart Bath Cookie Snickerdoodle Scent
description:
Yummy little cookies but don’t eat them! Drop them in your tub for a great scented and moisturizing bath. 
Bath cookies look good enough to eat but they are made from salt and fragrant oils. Makes a really interesting and unique gift, and works really well (like a solid bath salt). You get 3 heart sahped bath cookies all packaged for gift giving in heart bags!
Scented in Snickerdoodle!
Simply place in your bath and it will dissolve you may have to break it up a little!

name: Brownie Sundae Candle
description: This is a brownie candle topped with a scoop of vanilla scented ice cream , marshmellows & hot fudge fudge in a 5” aluminum tin. A wonderful dessert without the calories!
